PrecisTransfer to the Department of the SECRETARY OF STATE OF CANADA of the control and supervision of the CANADIAN PARKS SERVICE, SPORT CANADA, the INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS and MAJOR GAMES DIRECTORATE, and the OFFICE FOR THE 1994 COMMONWEALTH GAMES, and transfer to the Secretary of State of all the powers, duties and functions of the Minister of MULTICULTURALISM AND CITIZENSHIP and the Minister of COMMUNICATIONS, and AMALGAMATE AND COMBINE the Department of Secretary of State of Canada, the Department of Multiculturalism and Citizenship and the Department of Communications under the Secretary of State of Canada.
